I&#39;d like to request the removal of Kevin Igoe from CFRG co-chair.<br>
<br>
The Crypto Forum Research Group is chartered to provide crypto advice<br>
to IETF Working Groups. =A0As CFRG co-chair for the last 2 years, Kevin<br>
